== AGENT 

Aarhus University in collaboration with Tampere University and the Finnish Environment Institute

== GOAL

To recognize the identity of photographers based on the content of photos taken by them.

== DATA

Publicly available Finnish Wartime Photograph Archive containing around 160,000 photographs from Finnish Winter, Continuation, and Lapland Wars captured in 1939-1945

== METHODS

Supervised learning

== RESULTS

The AI model was able to achieve an average accuracy of 41.1 percent.

